<L>__{interior bank headquarters, executive offices day}
<A>__{sam and carl, laughing, walk through a large office area bustling with activity. employees, in various cubicles, are talking on telephones and punching information into computers. sam heads into his executive office. carl steps into a cubicle across the aisle. rose, sam's secretary, approaches him.}
<C>__{rose}
<D>__{morning, mr. wheat.}
